To active this module remember first: edit /etc/security/bluesscan.conf, 
if you don't know or don't remember any field, you can execute 
"hcitool scan" for get more info about your(s) bluetooth devices,
and second: edit /etc/pam.d/common-auth and line before pam_unix.so put
something like this   "auth  	 sufficient	  pam_blue.so" 

